                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Luxury to apprehend</l>
                    <l>The Luxury 'twould be </l>
                    <l>To look at Thee a<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 single time </l>
                    <l>An Epicure of Me </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>In whatsoever Presence<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 makes</l>
                    <l>Till for a further Food </l>
                    <l>I scarcely recollect to<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 starve </l>
                    <l>So first am I supplied -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Luxury to meditate </l>
                    <l>The Luxury it was</l>
                    <l>To banquet on thy<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Countenance </l>
                    <l>A Sumptuousness bestows </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>On plainer Days, whose<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Table far </l>
                    <l>As Certainty can see </l>
                    <l>Is laden with a single<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Crumb</l>
                    <l>The Consciousness of Thee.  </l>
                </lg>

